timing_librar...e_receiver_cap(25.10)    timing_librar...e_receiver_cap(25.10)

Name
       timing_library_use_two_piece_receiver_cap

Syntax
       timing_library_use_two_piece_receiver_cap {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables  the  use  of 2-piece receiver capacitance constructs, if a li-
       brary contains both the N-piece and 2-piece receiver  capacitance  con-
       struct.

       When  set to true, if a library has 2-piece and multi-piece pin capaci-
       tance, then the software gives priority to 2-piece models.

       When set to false, the software reads the N-piece receiver  capacitance
       constructs.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

